Package: FibroDynMix
Title: Hierarchical Bayesian Dynamic Mixture Models for Fibroblast Plasticity
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("FibroDynMix", "Developers", email = "dev@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: FibroDynMix Developers [aut, cre]
Maintainer: FibroDynMix Developers <dev@example.com>
Description: Simulation and modeling utilities for FibroDynMix, a
    hierarchical negative-binomial generative framework for fibroblast
    state mixtures, cohort effects, marker-program recovery, and transition
    flow inference from single-cell count data.
